# Bernd Rellermeyer <100.41728@germanynet.de>, 1998/7/11.

Format 58
Input scrclass.inc

SecNumDepth		3
TocDepth		3

NoStyle Chapter
NoCounter chapter
NoStyle Chapter*
NoStyle Addchap
NoStyle Addchap*
NoStyle Addpart
NoStyle Dictum


Style Part
	Align		Left
	TopSep		2
	BottomSep	1.5
	Font
	  Size		Larger
	EndFont
End

Style Part*
	Align		Left
	TopSep		2
	BottomSep	1.5
	Font
	  Size		Larger
	EndFont
End
